1 0 0 1 66.00 288.00 Tm (- Treat every customer interaction as an activity on the customer timeline.) Tj
/F1 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 275.00 Tm (- Preserve tenant isolation at every API, query, file, job, event, and webhook boundary.) Tj
/F1 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 262.00 Tm (- Make every module extensible through custom fields, saved views, permissions, workflow) Tj
/F1 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 74.00 249.00 Tm (  events, audit logs, imports, exports, and API access.) Tj
/F1 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 236.00 Tm (- Use background jobs for long-running imports, exports, automation, email sends,) Tj
/F1 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 74.00 223.00 Tm (  enrichment, AI analysis, and report generation.) Tj
/F1 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 210.00 Tm (- Avoid enterprise features that are just UI labels. Each feature should have persistence,) Tj
/F1 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 74.00 197.00 Tm (  permissions, auditability, and measurable workflow value.) Tj
